            <TextArea editable="false" layoutX="6.0" layoutY="52.0" prefHeight="288.0" prefWidth="588.0" stylesheets="@../application.css" text="Welcome to Tatai!&#10;&#10;Pick a game mode to start playing.&#10;&#10;Number: Tests you on your ability to read and pronounce numbers. You will be given numbers which you must read and translate into Maori.&#10;Equation: Tests your ability to work out mathematical equations. You must work out the answer to the equation first before saying the answer out loud in Maori. &#10;&#10;In both game modes you are given the choice to play one of three levels: easy, hard and custom.&#10;&#10;Easy: Primarily tests you on numbers 1~9&#10;Hard: Tests you on numbers 1~99&#10;Custom: Gives you the freedom to test yourself in any number or equation of your choice&#10;&#10;Once you pick a difficulty, press record  to start recording your voice. You will have 2 seconds to say the number on the screen in Maori. After you have finished recording, you will have the options to listen to your recording and to submit your recording to be marked. &#10;&#10;If your answer is correct, you will go on to the next question. &#10;&#10;If you are incorrect, you will have one more try at the same question.&#10;&#10;Good luck and have fun!" wrapText="true" />
